Backup Mail Server with DNS Replication Scripts!  
----------------------------------------------------------------
  
-> Change Path Variables at the top of the Cronjob Scripts if needed  
-> Change Config.php Settings  
-> Get sure permissions for webinterface files are right for webserver user
-> Change the Postfix Configuration to use Relaydomains  
-> Change DNS Settings to be a Slave with can replicate!  
-> Set up Cronjobs to be Executed
(see example config files for bind and postfix and cronjobs)  

Default Login is
----------------------------------------------------------------
Username: admin
Passwort: logmein



Ranks Are
----------------------------------------------------------------
user -> can enter domains 
user -> can enter server
admin -> can enter users

